text:
httpd-2.2.0 mod_proxy does not reuse connection pool. So, connection pool does 
not be used at all actually, it's only a waste of the system resource. The 
description related to mod_proxy's connection pool should be deleted from the 
document.

proxy_util.c line1851-1861
/*
 * TODO: Check if the connection can be reused
 */
if (conn->connection) {
    if (conn->sock) {
        apr_socket_close(conn->sock);
        conn->sock = NULL;
    }
    apr_pool_cleanup_kill(conn->connection->pool, conn, connection_cleanup);
    conn->connection = NULL;
}
